WEBVTT

00:04.726 --> 00:06.511
[Noah] Previously on The Affair...

00:06.512 --> 00:08.511
Author of the best-selling
novel, Descent,

00:08.512 --> 00:11.135
soon to be made into a
major motion picture,

00:11.136 --> 00:12.761
Noah Solloway.

00:12.762 --> 00:14.761
People know my movies, and
they see me as this, um,

00:14.762 --> 00:16.511
you know, this action hero,

00:16.512 --> 00:18.506
this sort of modern-day James Bond.

00:18.507 --> 00:19.719
But that's all an act, of course.

00:19.720 --> 00:21.665
I mean, that's not who I am.

00:21.666 --> 00:23.653
But this book, this is me.

00:23.654 --> 00:26.153
So what's your plan to make money?

00:26.154 --> 00:27.848
Ugh, I don't know.

00:27.849 --> 00:31.081
His visa's about to expire,
so no one will hire him.

00:31.082 --> 00:33.464
I just wanted to say I
think it's so awesome

00:33.465 --> 00:35.105
that you're my dad's girlfriend.

00:36.293 --> 00:37.511
Can I trouble you for another drink?

00:37.512 --> 00:40.135
[scoffs] Of course. Coming right up.

00:40.136 --> 00:41.886
[Noah] There's something wrong with him.

00:41.887 --> 00:44.037
He's losing his memory. He thinks
I'm still married to Helen.

00:44.038 --> 00:45.317
He thinks I own this place.

00:45.318 --> 00:47.220
[exhales] I need to leave.

00:49.345 --> 00:50.470
Come in.

00:52.220 --> 00:54.302
Vik, this is your son.

00:54.303 --> 00:56.094
This is Eddie.

00:56.095 --> 00:57.844
[Eddie coos softly]

00:57.845 --> 00:59.094
Are you with the studio?

00:59.095 --> 01:00.427
[scoffs] No.

01:00.428 --> 01:01.640
S-So you're...

01:01.641 --> 01:02.803
Helen.

01:02.804 --> 01:05.260
I lost my partner a few
months ago. [crying]

01:05.260 --> 01:07.052
Oh, my God.

01:07.053 --> 01:08.618
Just breathe.

01:08.619 --> 01:10.979
- I lost someone, too.
- [Paul] Where are you gonna stay?

01:10.980 --> 01:12.010
Dad's place.

01:12.011 --> 01:14.011
[Paul] Is that a good idea?

